<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.7">
<l>curikuḻal kaṉivāyt tiruviṉaip piritta koṭumaiyiṟ kaṭuvicai yarakkaṉ</l>
<l>eriviḻit tilaṅku maṇimuṭi poṭicey tilaṅkaipāḻ paṭuppataṟ keṇṇi</l>
<l>varicilai vaḷaiya vaṭucaran turantu maṟikaṭal neṟipaṭa malaiyāl</l>
<l>arikulam paṇikoṇ ṭalaikaṭa laṭaittā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam is the one who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having made ash of the jeweled crowns which shown glittering like fire</l>
<l>Of the demon with intense haste in wickedness who abducted Tiru</l>
<l rend="indent">of fruit-like lips and twisting curls,</l>
<l>Having determined to lay waste to Lanka, shooting a burning arrow</l>
<l rend="indent">as he bent his striped bow,</l>
<l>Dammed the crashing sea, having the help of the monkey clan with boulders</l>
<l rend="indent">so [there was] a path in the rising sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
